Subject: [PATCH 08/16] MPILIB: Reinstate mpi_cmp[_ui]() and export for RSA signature verification
Git-commit: 12f008b6dc5ff1c822fdb2198d20e3dbdc92f3f5
Patch-mainline: v3.7-rc1
References: fate#314508
Target: SLE-11 SP3

Reinstate and export mpi_cmp() and mpi_cmp_ui() from the MPI library for use by
RSA signature verification as per RFC3447 section 5.2.2 step 1.

Signed-off-by: David Howells <dhowells@redhat.com>
